                <div class='text-size-regular text-weight-semibold'>Week 5</div>
              </div>
              <div class='plan_tag-line is-bottom'></div>
            </div>
            <div data-figma-id='8907:32786' class='plan_card-wrapper'>
              <div data-figma-id='8907:32787' class='plan_card-content'>
                <div data-figma-id='8907:32788' class='plan_card-header'>
                  <h3 data-figma-id='8907:32789' class='text-size-large is-plan'>
                    Finish &amp; Feel Transformed
                  </h3>
                  <p data-figma-id='8907:32790' class='text-size-regular'>
                    Now
                    <strong>discipline feels natural</strong>, your mind clears, and your decisions move you toward what truly drives progress.
